# Pulumi Secrets Directory

This directory contains user-provided secrets for Pulumi deployments.
All JSON files (except templates) are **gitignored** for security.

## Directory Structure

```
_secrets/
├── credentials.template.json   # Template (committed to git)
├── staging.json                # Staging secrets (gitignored)
├── production.json             # Production secrets (gitignored)
└── README.md                   # This file
```

## Quick Start

1. **Copy the template:**

   ```bash
   cd iac/pulumi/src/_secrets
   cp credentials.template.json staging.json
   # Edit staging.json with your actual values
   ```

2. **Run the secret setter:**
   ```bash
   cd iac/pulumi
   ./scripts/pulumi-secret-set.sh -e staging
   ```

